;An Important Change in Firefox: Dedicated Profiles
Važna promjena u Firefoxu: Odvojeni profili


;What’s Changed
Što se promijenilo


;Before, all Firefox installations were sharing a single profile by default. Now, Firefox provides dedicated profiles for each Firefox installation (this includes installations of Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, or Firefox ESR). This will make Firefox more stable when switching between Firefox installations on the same computer.
Prije su sve Firefoxove instalacije standardno dijelile jedan profil. Sada Firefox nudi namjenske profile za svaku Firefox instalaciju (to uključuje instalacije za Firefox noćno izdanje, Firefox beta izdanje ili Firefox ESR). To čini Firefox stabilnijim prilikom prebacivanja između Firefox instalacija na istom računalu.


;How Dedicated Profiles Work
Kako rade odvojeni profili


;Firefox saves information such as bookmarks, passwords and user preferences in a set of files called your profile. This profile is stored in a separate location from the Firefox program files.
Firefox sprema podatke poput oznaka, lozinki i korisničkih postavki u skup datoteka koji čine tvoj profil. Ovaj se profil sprema na zasebnom mjestu u odnosu na Firefoxove programske datoteka.


;The installation you choose as your primary Firefox installation will keep your previously shared profile data like bookmarks, history and passwords.
Instalacija koju odabereš za svoju primarnu Firefox instalaciju sačuvat će tvoje prethodno dijeljene podatke profila kao što su oznake, povijest i lozinke.


;You have not lost any personal data or customizations. Any previous profile data is safe and attached to the first Firefox installation that was opened after this change.
Ne gubiš nikoje osobne podatke ili prilagodbe. Svi prethodni podaci profila sigurni su i priloženi prvoj instalaciji Firefoxa koja se otvori nakon ove promjene.


;All of your Firefox installations will now have separate profiles.
Sve tvoje Firefox instalacije će imati zasebne profile.


;What You Need to Do
Što ti moraš uraditi


;If you do nothing, each installation will have a separate profile. This means your profile data will be different on each installation of Firefox.
Ako ne učiniš ništa, svaka instalacija imat će zaseban profil. To znači da će se podaci tvog profila razlikovati pri svakoj instalaciji Firefoxa.


;You can change which installation uses which profile using the profile manager. Directions on how to use the profile manager are available on <a href="%(support)s">this support page</a>.
Pomoću upravljača profila možeš promijeniti profil za svaku instalaciju zasebno. Upute za korištenje upravljača profila dostupne su na <a href="%(support)s">ovoj stranici za podršku</a>.


;While profiles are now connected to each installation of Firefox, you can use your Firefox Account to keep them in sync. If you would like all of your profile data to be the same on all installations of Firefox, we recommend you sync all of your profiles with a Firefox Account.
Iako su profili sada povezani sa svakom Firefox instalacijom, možeš koristiti svoj Firefox račun kako bi ih držao/la sinkronizirano. Ako želiš da svi tvoji podaci profila budu isti na svim instalacijama Firefoxa, preporučujemo sinkronizirati sve vlastite profile s Firefox računom.


;A Firefox Account is the easiest way to make your profiles consistent on all of your versions of Firefox. You also get additional benefits like sending tabs and secure password storage.
Firefox račun je najlakši način za držanje profila dosljednima u svim tvojim verzijama Firefoxa. Uz to dobivaš razne dodatne pogodnosti, poput slanja kartica i sigurnog spremanja lozinki.


;You’re signed in and ready to start using Sync.
Tvoja je prijava uspjela i možeš koristiti sinkronizaciju.


;We detected that you have installed and opened an older version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Otkrili smo da je na tvom računalu instalirana i otvorena starija verzija Firefoxa. Možda ćeš morati nešto poduzeti.


;We detected more than one version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Otkrili smo više verzija Firefoxa na tvom računalu. Možda ćeš morati nešto poduzeti.


